nodes.label: message
nodes.text: Good Morning   Last night I went to the Org2 ED. The consensus is I had asthma attacks. I told them of this pain on my right side. It is intermittent and sharp, located right under my right breast to my right side. They said it may be muscle spasms. I just wanted you to know. I also was prescribed steriods for the asthma. Can I take that with the Ibrance? Should I start Ibrance tonight? Lots of words for a MM/DD/YYYY morning, thank you for your time.
